skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess game
des:
Alexa will give the definition of a word and you must guess what the word is.
If the user answer correctly, Alexa will tell you a fun fact related to the word.

If you need help, you can just ask and Alexa will give you the help you need.

With new words coming all the time, the fun and the learning will never end!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
